## 7. launchd 配置

> **用户无需手动编辑 XML**。修改 `.env` 中的 `SEND_HOUR` / `SEND_MINUTE` 后，运行 `python scripts/update_launchd.py` 即可自动生成 plist 并重新加载。

```xml
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN"
  "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
<dict>
    <key>Label</key>
    <string>com.dividend.notifier</string>
    <key>ProgramArguments</key>
    <array>
        <string>/path/to/venv/bin/python</string>
        <string>/path/to/dividend-notifier/scripts/daily_job.py</string>
    </array>
    <key>StartCalendarInterval</key>
    <dict>
        <key>Hour</key><integer>8</integer>    <!-- 从 .env SEND_HOUR 自动生成 -->
        <key>Minute</key><integer>30</integer>  <!-- 从 .env SEND_MINUTE 自动生成 -->
    </dict>
    <key>StandardOutPath</key>
    <string>/path/to/dividend-notifier/logs/stdout.log</string>
    <key>StandardErrorPath</key>
    <string>/path/to/dividend-notifier/logs/stderr.log</string>
    <key>EnvironmentVariables</key>
    <dict>
        <key>PATH</key>
        <string>/usr/local/bin:/usr/bin:/bin</string>
    </dict>
</dict>
</plist>
```

安装命令：
```bash
# 初次安装
python scripts/update_launchd.py

# 修改 .env 推送时间后，重新运行即可
python scripts/update_launchd.py
```

